Place the sliced mushrooms and aubergines in a microwave safe bowl. Drizzle over the olive oil and season with salt and freshly ground black pepper. Cover with cling film and microwave on high for 2 minutes, until the mushrooms and aubergines have steamed and are tender.Let them cool slightly, then pile onto the sliced roll. Top with the roasted pepper, mozzarella and red onion. Season with a pinch of dried oregano and pile on the rocket.